query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_depois,
  COUNT(DISTINCT cnpj) as cnpjs_unicos,
  COUNT(*) - COUNT(DISTINCT cnpj) as duplicatas_restantes,
  SUM(CASE WHEN DATE(createdAt) = '2025-10-21' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as originais_restantes,
  SUM(CASE WHEN DATE(createdAt) = '2025-11-19' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as enriquecidos_restantes,
  ROUND(AVG(qualidadeScore), 2) as score_medio_geral
FROM clientes 
WHERE cnpj IS NOT NULL AND cnpj != '';
